text: High Society Blues is a 1930 American romantic musical movie directed by David Butler and starring Janet Gaynor, Charles Farrell, William Collier, Sr., Hedda Hopper, Joyce Compton, Brandon Hurst. It was distributed by 20th Century Fox. ==Other websites== * * Category:1930 musical movies Category:1930 romance movies Category:American musical movies Category:American romance movies Category:20th Century Fox movies Category:Movies directed by David Butler
